'''扎赫拉·内玛提'''（{{lang-fa|زهرا نعمتی}}，{{bd|1985年|4月30日||}}）生于克尔曼省克尔曼市，是一名伊朗残疾射箭运动员。她在伤残前原本是一名[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]运动员。在[[2012年夏季残奥会射箭比赛|2012年伦敦残奥会]]中，她为伊朗收获一枚个人金牌和一枚团体铜牌。4年后她同时获得2016年里约奥运和2016年里约残奥的参赛资格<ref name="bbc20160125">{{cite news|title=Iran Paralympic archer Zahra Nemati to carry Olympic flag|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/disability-sport/35404284|accessdate=2016-05-02|work=BBC Sport|date=2016-01-25|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309015014/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/disability-sport/35404284|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
内玛提原本是一名[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]运动员，然而2003年发生的一场交通事故使她的[[脊髓|脊髓]]受到损伤，她也因此坐上轮椅<ref>{{cite news|title=Iran archer defies odds|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090917/jsp/sports/story_11505736.jsp|accessdate=2016-05-02|work=The Telegraph India|date=2009-09-17|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602130214/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090917/jsp/sports/story_11505736.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Iran's Zahra NEMATI wins individual SportAccord award|url=http://worldarchery.org/news/101503/irans-zahra-nemati-wins-individual-sportaccord-award|publisher=[[国际射箭联合会|World Archery Federation]]|accessdate=2016-05-03|date=2013-05-30|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602063231/http://worldarchery.org/news/101503/irans-zahra-nemati-wins-individual-sportaccord-award|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Shaking off quake blues, this Iranian archer will shoot from her wheelchair|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/shaking-off-quake-blues-this-iranian-archer-will-shoot-from-her-wheelchair/518057/|accessdate=2016-05-03|work=The Indian Express|date=2014-09-17|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723171843/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/shaking-off-quake-blues-this-iranian-archer-will-shoot-from-her-wheelchair/518057/}}</ref>。她在2006年开始练习射箭，半年后她便在全国锦标赛上和健全选手同台竞技，最终获得第3名<ref name="award">{{cite web|title=Iran's Zahra Nemati Individual Winner of 2013 Spirit of Sport Awards|url=https://www.paralympic.org/video/irans-zahra-nemati-individual-winner-2013-spirit-sport-awards|publisher=International Paralympic Committee|accessdate=2016-05-02|archive-date=2016-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508072602/https://www.paralympic.org/video/irans-zahra-nemati-individual-winner-2013-spirit-sport-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年，内玛提入选2012年夏季残奥伊朗代表团，比赛期间，她赢得了两枚奖牌，首先她在个人反曲弓轮椅1/2级项目上一路过关斩将摘得金牌，成为首位获得残奥金牌的伊朗女选手<ref name="tasnim">{{cite news|title=Zahra Nemati Named Iran Flagbearer at Olympics|url=http://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2016/01/23/978587/zahra-nemati-named-iran-flagbearer-at-olympics|accessdate=2016-05-02|work=Tasnim News Agency|date=2016-01-23|archive-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509010800/https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2016/01/23/978587/zahra-nemati-named-iran-flagbearer-at-olympics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。夺冠后，她称她要将这枚金牌献给所有祈求她能够获得成功的人们<ref>{{cite news|title=Iran's Zahra Nemati wins archery gold at 2012 Paralympics|url=http://www.payvand.com/news/12/sep/1029.html|accessdate=2016-05-02|work=Tehran Times|publisher=Payvand News|date=2012-09-04|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609180141/http://www.payvand.com/news/12/sep/1029.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在之后进行的女子团体反曲弓项目上，她联同队友[[Razieh_Shir_Mohammadi|Razieh Shir Mohammadi]]和[[Zahra_Javanmard|Zahra Javanmard]]再为伊朗斩获一枚铜牌<ref>{{cite web|title=Wheelchair-bound Hijabi Athletes Reach Targets in London|url=https://www.aquila-style.com/focus-points/paralympics-2012/19430/|publisher=Aquila Style|accessdate=2017-10-05|date=2012-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005202305/https://www.aquila-style.com/focus-points/paralympics-2012/19430/|archive-date=2017-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年11月，她在[[泰国|泰国]][[曼谷|曼谷]]举办的[[2015年亚洲射箭锦标赛|亚洲射箭锦标赛]]上获得奥运资格<ref>{{cite web|url=https://worldarchery.org/news/132294/first-rio-2016-continental-qualifier-adds-5-more-nations-asia|title=First Rio 2016 continental qualifier adds 5 more nations from Asia|publisher=World Archery Federation|date=2015-11-08|accessdate=2016-07-29|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806135111/https://worldarchery.org/news/132294/first-rio-2016-continental-qualifier-adds-5-more-nations-asia|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成为继意大利选手[[保拉·凡塔托|保拉·凡塔托]]之后又一位同时获得奥运和残奥参赛资格的射箭运动员。2016年1月，她获选为[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会伊朗代表团|2016年夏季奥运伊朗代表团]][[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會入場旗手|开幕式旗手]]<ref name="bbc20160125"/>。在[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會女子個人射箭比賽|奥运正赛]]中，她被俄罗斯选手[[Inna_Stepanova|Inna Stepanova]]淘汰，止步64强<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/09/zahra-nemati-olympics-heart-and-minds-archery|title=Trail-blazer Zahra Nemati wins hearts and minds with stirring effort in archery|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2016-08-09|accessdate=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005202827/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/09/zahra-nemati-olympics-heart-and-minds-archery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

里约奥运过后，她继续征战残奥。比赛期间，她共获得一枚金牌和一枚银牌。首先她在团体赛中联同队友[[Ebrahim_Ranjbarkivaj|Ebrahim Ranjbarkivaj]]获得团体反曲弓公开级银牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iransportspress.com/iranian-paralympic-archers-ranjbarkivaj-and-nemati-win-silver-medals-in-rio/|title=Iranian Paralympic archers Ranjbarkivaj and Nemati win silver medals in Rio|publisher=Iran Sports Press|date=2016-09-12|accessdate=2017-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005201916/http://iransportspress.com/iranian-paralympic-archers-ranjbarkivaj-and-nemati-win-silver-medals-in-rio/|archive-date=2017-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，之后她又在女子个人反曲弓公开级项目上夺得金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.com/Detail/2016/09/16/484896/Iran-archer-Zahra-Nemati-gold-javelin-throw-Mohsen-Kaedi-Javad-Hardani|title=Nemati earns Iran's 7th gold medal at Rio 2016 Paralympics|date=2016-09-16|accessdate=2017-10-05|publisher=PressTV|archive-date=2017-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004202143/http://presstv.com/Detail/2016/09/16/484896/Iran-archer-Zahra-Nemati-gold-javelin-throw-Mohsen-Kaedi-Javad-Hardani|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年，内玛提同时获得亚洲运动会和亚洲残疾人运动会的参赛资格，得以首次参加亚运<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2018/06/19/1753191/zahra-nemati-to-represent-iran-in-asian-games|title=Zahra Nemati to Represent Iran in Asian Games|publisher=Tasnim News Agency|date=2018-06-19|accessdate=2019-09-20|archive-date=2020-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107003619/https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2018/06/19/1753191/zahra-nemati-to-represent-iran-in-asian-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在8月进行的亚洲运动会中，她出战女子个人反曲弓和混合团体反曲弓两个项目，均进入16强<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocagames.com/orb/files/4/61/AG2018_OfficialResultBook_Archery_v1.0.pdf|title=Official Result Book – Archery|work=OCA|accessdate=2019-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904021938/http://www.ocagames.com/orb/files/4/61/AG2018_OfficialResultBook_Archery_v1.0.pdf|archivedate=2018-09-04}}</ref>。之后她出战亚洲残疾人运动会，获得混合团体反曲弓公开级金牌和个人反曲弓公开级银牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.mehrnews.com/news/138576/Iranian-archers-win-gold-silver-in-team-event|title=Iranian archers win gold, silver in team event|publisher=Mehr News Agency|date=2018-10-11|accessdate=2019-09-20|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920083013/https://en.mehrnews.com/news/138576/Iranian-archers-win-gold-silver-in-team-event|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://worldarchery.org/news/164682/china-dominates-archery-events-asian-para-games-jakarta|title=China dominates archery events at Asian Para Games in Jakarta|work=World Archery|date=2018-10-25|accessdate=2019-09-20|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920083021/https://worldarchery.org/news/164682/china-dominates-archery-events-asian-para-games-jakarta|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

